OL,7,FA second journalist sued by Sinn Fein
OL,8,FMLA Gerry Kelly for claiming he shot a
OL,9,Fprison officer has vowed not to be
OL,10,Fsilenced after the libel action was
OL,11,Fended.
OL,13,FProceedings brought against Ruth
OL,14,FDudley Edwards over a statement about
OL,15,FMr Kelly's role during a mass escape
OL,16,Ffrom the Maze Prison more than 40
OL,17,Fyears ago were dismissed by consent.
