OL,7,FMs Dudley Edwards, a prominent writer
OL,8,Fand critic of Sinn Fein, said her
OL,9,Flegal costs are to be paid under the
OL,10,Fterms of the settlement.
OL,12,FFollowing the outcome, she pledged to
OL,13,Fcontinue speaking out.
OL,15,F"I will never give in... I care very
OL,16,Fpassionately about free speech," she
OL,17,Finsisted.
