OL,4,Csilenced after libel action was struck
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FEarlier this year a separate libel
OL,8,Faction Mr Kelly took against writer
OL,9,Fand journalist Malachi O'Doherty was
OL,10,Fthrown out at the High Court in
OL,11,FBelfast.
OL,13,FA judge declared that case to be
OL,14,F"scandalous, frivolous, and vexatious"
OL,15,Fand ordered the Sinn Fein politician
OL,16,Fto foot the legal bill for the case.
OL,18,FAlthough proceedings against Ms Dudley
OL,19,FEdwards initially continued, it was
OL,20,Fconfirmed today that a settlement has
OL,21,Fbeen reached.
