OL,7,FA final order was made on terms agreed
OL,8,Fbetween the parties without any
OL,9,Fwritten judgment.
OL,11,FPrison officer John Adams was shot in
OL,12,Fthe head during the mass break-out
OL,13,Ffrom the Maze by IRA inmates in 1983.
OL,15,FMr Kelly was later prosecuted but
OL,16,Fultimately acquitted of the shooting.
OL,18,FHe had previously been convicted on
OL,19,Fexplosive charges related to the IRA
OL,20,Fbomb attack on the Old Bailey court
OL,21,Fbombing in London in 1973.
