OL,7,FHe sued Dr O'Doherty for libel over
OL,8,Fcomments made in two radio interviews
OL,9,Fin August 2019.
OL,11,FDuring the programmes the journalist
OL,12,Falleged that Mr Kelly had shot the
OL,13,Fwarder in the head.
OL,15,FIt was claimed that those comments
OL,16,Fgravely damaged the Sinn Fein
OL,17,Frepresentative's character and
OL,18,Freputation.
