OL,4,Csilenced after libel action was struck
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FHis standing as a respected public
OL,8,Frepresentative and MLA for North
OL,9,FBelfast had been called into
OL,10,Fdisrepute, according to the defamation
OL,11,Faction.
OL,13,FAn application to have that action
OL,14,Fstruck out cited material contained in
OL,15,FMr Kelly's autobiographies.
OL,17,FIn January, Master Bell held that the
OL,18,Fdescription of events in the
OL,19,Fpolitician's books demonstrated a
OL,20,F"common design", regardless of who
OL,21,Ffired the shot.
