OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FDr O'Doherty was deemed to have
OL,8,Festablished a complete defence to a
OL,9,Flawsuit found to be untenable.
OL,11,FMaster Bell said at the time: "Even if
OL,12,Fone accepts the submission that Mr
OL,13,FKelly has not explicitly admitted
OL,14,Fpulling the trigger, the content of
OL,15,Fhis books appears to make Mr Kelly
OL,16,Fcivilly liable, on the balance of
OL,17,Fprobabilities, for the shooting of Mr
OL,18,FAdams."
